  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\" property=\"schema:text\"><p> </p><p><strong>Presented by BlackRock</strong></p><p><span>The movement of people and goods over land represents about 12% of global greenhouse gas emissions. Enabled by recent advances in battery energy storage, we believe the electrification of road transport will be central in the transition to a low-carbon economy.</span></p><p><a href=\"https://www.internationalinsurance.org/sites/default/files/2024-01/Transition%20Center%20of%20Expertise-Mobility-Land_STAMPED.pdf\"><span><strong>Read more &gt;</strong></span></a></p></div></body></html>",
